            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Nanaca. What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11a,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "My Poro went missing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "What should I do? Juris told me to be careful..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Poro... That's the calf that has a big appetite, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I haven't seen her.<CR>Where did you last see her?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x121,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "On the way here from Hornheim. I lost sight of her before I even knew it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "She's a mischievous calf, but I still can't leave her by herself yet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "If stray dogs or wolves got her,<CR>I don't know what I'd do..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I'll look for her, too. If I find her, I'll catch her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x120,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Ayesha. Please do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Her name is Poro. But if you call her name, she'll start running away, so be careful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It seems like it'll be hard to catch her without calling her name...but, I'll do my best."
